</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="21">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhu-jian-qiao-5" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhu-jian-qiao-5" class="zg-link" title="朱剑桥">朱剑桥</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yao-qing-shu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yao-qing-shu" class="zg-link" title="坠吼是窝">坠吼是窝</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$Alex-Yang-EE" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/Alex-Yang-EE" class="zg-link" title="Alex Yang">Alex Yang</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2033900" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">这个图标叫Spikey，演化历程如下图：<br><br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/c1ed86a30633222c03720ee5db9f522f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="308" class="content_image" width="400"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="308" class="content_image lazy" width="400" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/c1ed86a30633222c03720ee5db9f522f_b.jpg"><br>最初版本是一个二十面体，是由60个正三角形组成的：<br><br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/71551792531717d094cd69afd1cafba7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="174" data-rawheight="174" class="content_image" width="174"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="174" data-rawheight="174" class="content_image lazy" width="174" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/71551792531717d094cd69afd1cafba7_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/5c04e74187126544df093dfd31f9fb16_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="310" data-rawheight="227" class="content_image" width="310"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="310" data-rawheight="227" class="content_image lazy" width="310" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/5c04e74187126544df093dfd31f9fb16_b.jpg"><br>共有32个顶点，90条边。<br><br>单位边长的Spikey，其表面积为<br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/57b47997f48fe032a131aa99c267f6da_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="68" data-rawheight="20" class="content_image" width="68">体积为</noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="68" data-rawheight="20" class="content_image lazy" width="68" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/57b47997f48fe032a131aa99c267f6da_b.jpg">体积为<br><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/0472e21e714d2e06fa691d619319de18_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="150" data-rawheight="24" class="content_image" width="150"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="150" data-rawheight="24" class="content_image lazy" width="150" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/0472e21e714d2e06fa691d619319de18_b.jpg"><br>从第二代开始，这个图形不断趋于复杂，像第二代的图形,就是一个双曲十二面体。<br><br>这个图形不能用函数表达，不过mathematica中有相应的命令PolyhedronData[”“]。<br><br>其他更简便的获得这个图标的方法：<br><a href="http://www.wolframalpha.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Wolfram|Alpha: Computational Knowledge Engine<i class="icon-external"></i></a><br><br>输入命令<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/08335d69f9fdaf8b7f0a153f0e4c889f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="666" data-rawheight="382" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="666" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/08335d69f9fdaf8b7f0a153f0e4c889f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="666" data-rawheight="382" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="666" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/08335d69f9fdaf8b7f0a153f0e4c889f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/08335d69f9fdaf8b7f0a153f0e4c889f_b.jpg">


</div>

</div>
