<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2033900" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">Michael Trott 写过一篇博客 <a href="http://blog.wolfram.com/2007/05/22/making-the-mathematica-6-spikey/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Making the Mathematica 6 Spikey<i class="icon-external"></i></a>， 介绍Mathematica 图标的来历。 文章后面有个notebook可以下载，里面有画Mathematica 6 图标的详细代码。 之前版本的图标的画法可以在他写的Mathematica guidebook 里面找到。<br><br><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/9c304f77c9940ae8003d39ad4c0161eb_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="300" data-rawheight="311" class="content_image" width="300">
<a href="/question/24629531/answer/41939080" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
